```
public static void bufferedOutputStream(
  String file, String ...data) throws IOException {

    try (BufferedOutputStream out = new BufferedOutputStream(new FileOutputStream(file))) {
        for(String s : data) {
            out.write(s.getBytes());
            out.write(" ".getBytes());
        }
    }
}
```

